    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148090/extras/a68927ebe5639cfe0138870b14d625cf.poster.avif?t=1772183865\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148090/extras/a68927ebe5639cfe0138870b14d625cf.webm?t=1772183865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148090/extras/a68927ebe5639cfe0138870b14d625cf.mp4?t=1772183865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Safe Haven</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are offered a place inside a safe house during a mysterious outbreak. <br>Strangers beg for help and supplies are running out. <br>A mysterious man on the radio guides you and tests your character, but his motives are unclear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148090/extras/69d1097bd896878ab4634a13c6853a31.poster.avif?t=1772183865\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148090/extras/69d1097bd896878ab4634a13c6853a31.webm?t=1772183865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148090/extras/69d1097bd896878ab4634a13c6853a31.mp4?t=1772183865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Do what you have to do</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every day you have to make decisions:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who to help;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How to ration food, medicine, and building materials;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trust the voice or ignore it;</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148090/extras/a2523265a6a8b407de104bb7eaff5c50.poster.avif?t=1772183865\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148090/extras/a2523265a6a8b407de104bb7eaff5c50.webm?t=1772183865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148090/extras/a2523265a6a8b407de104bb7eaff5c50.mp4?t=1772183865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you truly safe?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even inside the safe house, danger is everywhere. Raiders will try to break in, others may try to poison your air filtration, and the generator could fail at the worst possible moment. You need to act. And act fast.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148090/extras/061b78a5bc8ce59217d355e0a116fdb4.poster.avif?t=1772183865\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148090/extras/061b78a5bc8ce59217d355e0a116fdb4.webm?t=1772183865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148090/extras/061b78a5bc8ce59217d355e0a116fdb4.mp4?t=1772183865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspirations:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay: No, I'm Not a Human, 60 Seconds!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cutscenes: As Dusk Falls, Max Payne 1-2</p></li></ul>",
